inations Nominees |access-date=2010-03-12 |archive-date=2010-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101220125841/http://oscar.go.com/nominations/nominees?cid=10_oscars_landingCallout_nominations&cid=10_oscars_rightrail_nominations#category_documentary-feature |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

